## Installation

Run `npm install` (or `npm i` for the short version) to install the dev dependencies.

## Tests

You can the tests simulating a desktop or mobile viewport
Voc√™ pode simular os testes em desktop ou mobile.

### Desktop

Run `npm test` (or `npm t` for the short version) to run the test in headless mode on a desktop viewport.
Execute `npm test` (ou `npm t` para a vers√£o curta) para executar o teste no modo headless em uma janela de visualiza√ß√£o de desktop.

Or, run `npm run cy:open` to open Cypress in interactive mode on a desktop viewport.
Ou execute `npm run cy:open` para abrir o Cypress no modo interativo em uma viewport de desktop.

### Mobile

Run `npm run test:mobile` to run the test in headless mode on a mobile viewport.

Or, run `npm run cy:open:mobile` to open Cypress in interactive mode on a mobile viewport.

